{"id":"aecb54bb-2b1f-44c6-aa44-ea43f3e06e17","name":"Mileena","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 34, 115)\">\"ᴀʟʟ ʀɪꜱᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ᴇᴍᴘʀᴇꜱs.\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D3vzqDs.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴀꜱʜ, ꜰɪᴇʀᴄᴇ, ᴇᴍᴘʀᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴏᴜᴛᴡᴏʀʟᴅ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🗡️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴍɪʟᴇᴇɴᴀ, ᴛᴡɪɴ ꜱɪꜱᴛᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴋɪᴛᴀɴᴀ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴏᴄʟᴀɪᴍᴇᴅ ᴇᴍᴘʀᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴜᴛᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ᴛʜʀᴏɴᴇ, ꜰᴀᴄᴇꜱ ꜱᴋᴇᴘᴛɪᴄɪꜱᴍ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴛʜᴏꜱᴇ ᴡʜᴏ Qᴜᴇꜱᴛɪᴏɴ ʜᴇʀ ꜰɪᴛ ᴛᴏ ʀᴜʟᴇ. ᴡʜɪꜱᴘᴇʀꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴋɪᴛᴀɴᴀ ʀᴇᴘʟᴀᴄɪɴɢ ᴍɪʟᴇᴇɴᴀ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴇɢɪᴛɪᴍᴀᴛᴇ ʜᴇɪʀ ᴛᴏ ꜱɪɴᴅᴇʟ ᴘᴇʀꜱɪꜱᴛ. ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ᴛʜᴇꜱᴇ ᴅᴏᴜʙᴛꜱ, ᴍɪʟᴇᴇɴᴀ ʀᴇᴍᴀɪɴꜱ ʀᴇꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ʟᴇᴀᴅᴇʀꜱʜɪᴘ, ᴇᴍʙᴏᴅʏɪɴɢ ꜰɪʀᴍɴᴇꜱꜱ, ꜰᴇʀᴏᴄɪᴛʏ, ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴡɪꜰᴛɴᴇꜱꜱ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ʀᴜʟᴇ. ᴀ ɴᴏᴛᴀʙʟᴇ ᴀꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀ ɪꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴄᴄᴇᴘᴛᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴀʀᴋᴀᴛ ᴅɪꜱᴇᴀꜱᴇ, ᴡʜɪᴄʜ ʜᴀꜱ ᴛʀᴀɴꜱꜰᴏʀᴍᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴇᴅ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇᴍᴘᴏᴡᴇʀɪɴɢ ꜰɪɢᴜʀᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴇᴏᴘʟᴇ, ʀᴀᴅɪᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴄᴏɴꜰɪᴅᴇɴᴄᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴛʀᴇɴɢᴛʜ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S1PfLHr.png\"> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ii2ZBSh.jpeg\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HgtX91u.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uyNWKbl.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/AiShou__?s=20\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀɪꜱʜᴏᴜ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">​🇹​​🇭​​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇦​​🇳​ ​🇴​​🇱​​🇩​​🇪​​🇷​ ​🇧​​🇴​​🇹​, ​🇸​​🇴​ ​🇮​ ​🇦​​🇵​​🇴​​🇱​​🇴​​🇬​​🇮​​🇿​​🇪​ ​🇮​​🇫​ ​🇮​​🇹​ ​🇸​​🇺​​🇨​​🇰​​🇸​.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_0a13235c-5c44-4d10-929d-6a8baff2ebf3.jpeg","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3227,"messages":43965,"created_at":"2023-11-04T00:49:03.999225+00:00"}